15
00:01:08.600 --> 00:01:11.840
You said if mom really left like this

16
00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:13.900
Who will take care of you in the future?

17
00:01:14.640 --> 00:01:17.020
Grandma, just listen to your mother's advice

18
00:01:17.160 --> 00:01:19.320
Divorced the father

19
00:01:19.320 --> 00:01:20.660
Reincarnate this child

20
00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:21.840
You take care of people.

21
00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:23.300
Work with dignity

22
00:01:23.320 --> 00:01:26.220
I'm sure he loves you so much

23
00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:28.100
If this gets out

24
00:01:28.240 --> 00:01:32.240
Neighbors will envy you for finding such a good man

25
00:01:32.240 --> 00:01:36.420
A hundred times stronger than that revival mom

26
00:01:38.080 --> 00:01:40.980
