27
00:01:42.040 --> 00:01:44.860
Just be a mother, please, okay?

28
00:01:50.120 --> 00:01:50.940
OK

29
00:01:51.720 --> 00:01:53.020
I promise you.

30
00:01:53.880 --> 00:01:55.260
Divorce with father

